title: Rams-Seahawks TNF Preview (Football 10/3)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jared Dubin to preview Thursday's matchup between the Rams and Seahawks. The guys break down the state of the NFC West, concerns with Chris Carson, woes for Jared Goff and the Los Angeles offensive line before giving their picks and going over player props for the game.
